answers.answer: How Is your blood Pressure? AnY Severe Swelling In Your Feet And Ankles Or Headaches. I Had Preeclampsia With My Second Pregnancy. I Had No Other Symptoms Other Than A Little Dizzy And Seeing Stars Like Three Times. Please Check Your Blood Pressure And If It Is High Call Your Doctor. I Truly Hope You Start Feeling Better Soon And Good Luck!
